{"tid":893807,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"少年為救兄弟　自願獻身遭熊分屍慘死","createTime":"2018-11-08T02:29:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-08T06:13:10.000Z","uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":11,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"cdd72ec80c4b66baf2e4862874c284ad3eb335f2","tid":893807,"uid":122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:29:08.000Z","msg":"俄羅斯一名16歲少年羅迪翁(Rodion Burakov)，為了營救13歲堂弟博利斯(Boris Burakov)逃離熊的魔掌，竟然自願獻身，引開熊對博利斯的注意力，但最後羅迪翁不幸慘遭熊分屍。<br />\n<br />\n據英國《鏡報》報導，羅迪翁和博利斯兩人在做完桑拿浴之後，走到這處離家14公里遠的叢林，卻遇上一隻熊的攻擊。熊最初先攻擊博利斯，但羅迪翁隨即挑釁熊，引開熊對博利斯的注意力，熊轉而追逐羅迪翁，之後羅迪翁跑進森林中，自此之後博利斯再也看不見他的人影。<br />\n<br />\n博利斯隨即回村落通報，當地鄉民和獵人以及搜救人員全員出動，尋找羅迪翁的蹤跡，但最後仍傳來噩耗。一名女搜救人員最先在一處落葉枯枝底下，找到羅迪翁的殘肢，包括斷掉的下肢與手臂，他們相信熊把羅迪翁殺害後，當成「食物」藏起來，並把羅迪翁分屍。很快地，搜救人員就找到攻擊羅迪翁兄弟的熊，最後當場對牠射殺處死，據悉這頭熊的年齡約為3歲。<br />\n<br />\n當地媒體皆紛紛讚許羅迪翁捨身救弟的行為，直呼他是「英雄」，並相信當局將會對他追贈獎牌，感念他的英勇事蹟。（施旖婕／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.redd.it/4w5jtyrkbys11.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.redd.it%2F4w5jtyrkbys11.jpg&h=47966561&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n本人提供既示意圖"},{"pid":"3b1adfb8c07e935d1dcb52a15a3d13bbbbc2eddc","tid":893807,"uid":818,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:30:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a9b16960a882676213f8f17fcce2a83f2a0c7e2","tid":893807,"uid":132898,"like":7,"dislike":1,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:32:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> rip<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"468247f8c5215979682e1ef8ccb889563468e8d8","tid":893807,"uid":167566,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:32:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25262b92592967f41ba0bfdacc153707b24d84bb","tid":893807,"uid":50531,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:32:51.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bcd14632de2f89ad175dda0578b72ab64dc8aafb","tid":893807,"uid":180655,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:34:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b86cb0c4f0b6ef86995a2c558968b2a6cf44209d","tid":893807,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"走到14公里遠的森林？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43b409c5f102ad5ccce07bca5a974f05ee284c4f","tid":893807,"uid":202464,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:34:34.000Z","msg":"熊熊rip"},{"pid":"19b1241ced56e99ceadc0dc066e65fad5c336e06","tid":893807,"uid":34186,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:35:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"89dad07ba55a3024fa81d8f73fafdc3722400fec","tid":893807,"uid":70786,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:35:45.000Z","msg":"好兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/pokemon_1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8462985cffd421ffc1a2a3f66e7a37ab9788eec4","tid":893807,"uid":130901,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b86cb0c4f0b6ef86995a2c558968b2a6cf44209d","tid":893807,"uid":33206,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:34:15.000Z","msg":"走到14公里遠的森林？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:36:00.000Z","msg":"桑拿完行下山"},{"pid":"53b55c42672ae2c60bb4059b0ec9706f245360ad","tid":893807,"uid":49197,"like":20,"dislike":1,"score":19,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T02:36:27.000Z","msg":"從前，有兩個人在森林裡遇到了一隻熊。<br />\n第一個人就開始禱告。<br />\n第二個人則開始綁鞋帶。<br />\n第一個人就問他：「你為什麼要綁鞋帶？你又跑不贏那隻熊？」<br />\n第二個人就說：「我幹嘛跑贏那隻熊？我只要跑贏你就好啦！」"},{"pid":"f658ae9b4af7cc6dc1596d593975760bed9fcd43","tid":893807,"uid":67500,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T04:30:55.000Z","msg":"詠春有插眼架嘛，唔學中國人功夫，鬼佬渣GA"},{"pid":"35dc7ead33f7a12b73602ec0a067dadfd95f6b52","tid":893807,"uid":208159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-08T06:13:10.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}